Package: dpCustomFunctions
Title: Custom R Functions for CyTOF and Single-Cell Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Priest", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "david.priest@example.com")
Description: A collection of custom plotting and utility functions for CyTOF
    (mass cytometry) and single-cell RNA-seq analysis. Extends CATALYST and
    Seurat with additional visualisation functions, spillover QC tools, SCE
    manipulation helpers, division-profiling plots, and pipeline output
    utilities. Designed to work within a {targets} pipeline workflow.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
